{"tid":1275654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明早與電台盡訴心中情活動","createTime":"2019-07-01T21:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T23:32:54.000Z","uid":223934,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30bf70b2f3874900f864ea5b7c7aabce31456e10","tid":1275654,"uid":223934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:20:12.000Z","msg":"[url]可以扮中立人 中立L係香港有好多！<br />\n同朋友討論過 以下小小建議：<br />\n唔好提 警、暴、反、中 呢啲字眼<br />\n佢地一聽就起哂鋼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同盡量唔好講班黑警住 <br />\n<br />\n要重申係政府唔肯對話 先醞釀一連串嘅事件<br />\n其實淋病一個人已經可以解決所有問題<br />\n包括台灣案件 （人地有俾方法 但港府拒絕）<br />\n希望政府在逃犯條例修訂上持開放態度 聆聽不同意見和聲音<br />\n民主 自由 容納不同聲音<br />\n維護香港核心價值<br />\n<br />\n盡量節奏語調控制好 唔好太有個人感情<br />\n要不偏不倚 佢地最鍾意呢啲<br />\n<br />\n絕不割蓆 支持及保護義士[/url]"},{"pid":"b4ec879da8e579a5f80b936e14df6e8e2bf6460f","tid":1275654,"uid":223934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:22:11.000Z","msg":"屌 眼訓得濟 禁錯制<br />\n<br />\n詳細如下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽早盡力打入所有電台phone in節目，保住輿論<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275028</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要打去！"},{"pid":"444e755b4815d63df408c4e01f64bfb4a6ab7023","tid":1275654,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba48c1e6d35e2109cd2d8ef52b8b1123922410b","tid":1275654,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:14:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n將民意化做聲音！"},{"pid":"021bfe75c69d26bde7aa2f1bc0cec324057cb7be","tid":1275654,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.